    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade F80 M3 Competition, maintained to a standard that exceeds the factory PDI. This S55 powerplant exhibits zero deviation from peak boost parameters, benefiting from a strictly enforced 3,000-mile interval of Liqui Moly 5W-40. The 7-speed DCT has been recalibrated for lightning-quick, zero-lash engagement, paired with an Active M Differential that remains perfectly shimmed for optimal torque vectoring. Every bushing is silent, and the adaptive M suspension delivers a flat cornering profile with no hydraulic degradation. The paint correction and ceramic coating preserve a depth of finish that must be seen to be appreciated. This isn't just a car; it\u2019s a precision-engineered instrument with every mechanical tolerance verified and accounted for.",
